15. Qa4
15. Bxh2+ {Anyway!} 
16. Kxh2
16. Ng4+
17. Kh3 {Or17.Kg3Rg6.} 
17. Qc8 {Setting up a battery against White's king. The position is 0.00 according to Stockfish, but in reality White has to successfully navigate a minefield in order not to lose.} 
