13. Qe2 {This seems best. As the bishop wouldn't make much sense on g5 for reasons explained previously, White should go for a setup with c4 and Bb2, and then it makes sense to first gain a tempo on the a6-knight.} 
13. Nb8 {This knight has done its job and will now be rerouted to a5.} 
14. c4
